default6.2
default              
defaultIn terms of assurance on delivering broad value for money, HCC considers its procurement management approach, continuous improvement culture and controls highlighted in this submission as sound business “input” indicators. Ultimately, however, it is the delivery of outcomes for residents that are the best indicators of success, both in terms of customer satisfaction and Council Tax cost. HCC’s performance remains high in these key areas and it will strive hard to build on this.
default&#xa0;
default6.3
default              
defaultBy adopting this approach (and others) identified in this response, local authorities will have created a sustainable framework of issues to ensure value for money. Consistently challenging the framework and the issues ensures value for money is sustained. Capacity, competence, challenge and collaboration should be evident in any approach.default     
